column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.PSFMag_u - p.extinction_u as mu, p.PSFMag_g - p.extinction_g as mg, p.PSFMag_r - p.extinction_i as mr, p.PSFMag_i - p.extinction_i as mi, p.PSFMag_z - p.extinction_z as mz, p.psfmagerr_u as mue, p.psfmagerr_g as mge, p.psfmagerr_r as mre, p.psfmagerr_i as mie, p.psfmagerr_z as mze FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObj p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
